{"id": "figure_007", "modality": "figures", "name": "Latent Diffusion U-Net with Timestep + Text Cross-Attention", "task": {"description": "Create a single 1920x1080 self-contained HTML file using ONLY inline CSS and inline SVG that reproduces a Stable-Diffusion / Latent-Diffusion denoising U-Net figure. Title 'Latent Diffusion U-Net (with conditioning)' at top in 32px bold. Draw a U-shaped network: a LEFT descending encoder of FOUR down-blocks at decreasing spatial resolution (annotate resolutions 64x64, 32x32, 16x16, 8x8 and channel counts), a bottleneck 'mid-block' at the bottom, and a RIGHT ascending decoder of FOUR up-blocks mirroring the encoder. Draw FOUR horizontal skip connections from each encoder level to its mirror decoder level. INPUT (left) is a 'Noisy Latent z_t (4 x 64 x 64)' box; OUTPUT (right) is 'Predicted Noise \u03b5_\u03b8'. Two conditioning signals enter: (1) a 'Timestep t -> sinusoidal embedding -> MLP' box whose embedding is injected into EVERY block (draw labelled injection arrows into each down/up block), and (2) a 'Text Prompt -> CLIP Text Encoder' box feeding 'cross-attention' into the blocks (draw cross-attention arrows into at least the mid and adjacent blocks). Annotate which blocks contain 'ResBlock' vs 'ResBlock + Cross-Attn'. HARDEN (density + alignment): ALSO include (a) a LEGEND box that maps every distinct block color and every arrow/line style used in the figure, and (b) a small tensor-shape annotation on each major block (e.g. 'BxNxd'). Pack the figure densely with at least 14 labeled elements; every group of sibling blocks must be equal-size and share edges, with uniform gutters, and nothing may overlap or clip.", "requirements": ["All blocks (4 down-blocks, mid-block, 4 up-blocks), the timestep-embedding path, and the text/CLIP conditioning path are visible with no clipping at any edge", "No two blocks overlap each other", "Every block label text and resolution/channel annotation is fully contained inside its box with no overflow", "Exactly FOUR skip connections connect each encoder down-block to its mirror decoder up-block at the same depth and do not pass through the bottleneck or unrelated blocks", "The encoder down-blocks are drawn at decreasing spatial size and the decoder up-blocks mirror them at increasing size (U shape)", "The timestep-embedding path injects into the blocks via labelled arrows, and these injection arrows do not overlap each other or pass through unrelated blocks", "The text/CLIP cross-attention path feeds into the blocks via distinct labelled cross-attention arrows separate from the timestep arrows", "Resolution annotations (64x64, 32x32, 16x16, 8x8) appear on the correct encoder levels and are legible without colliding", "Input 'Noisy Latent z_t' and output 'Predicted Noise \u03b5_\u03b8' boxes are both present, labelled, and not overlapping", "Blocks containing cross-attention are labelled distinctly from plain ResBlocks", "No element is within 10px of any viewport edge", "No horizontal or vertical scrollbar appears; all content fits inside 1920x1080", "A legend box maps every block color and arrow/line style used; each major block carries a tensor-shape annotation; sibling blocks are equal-size and edge-aligned with uniform gutters; no element overlaps or is clipped"]}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 1, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 1, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 7205, "rv_n_defects": 1, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 1, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 35114}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 1, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 1, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 7110, "rv_n_defects": 1, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 1, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 35194}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 1, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 1, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 7480, "rv_n_defects": 1, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 1, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 34119}], "ss_img": "images/figures/figure_007_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/figures/figure_007_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Latent Diffusion U-Net</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"title\">Latent Diffusion U-Net (with conditioning)</div>\n    \n    <svg width=\"1880\" height=\"1000\" viewBox=\"0 0 1880 1000\">\n        <!-- Background -->\n        <rect width=\"1880\" height=\"1000\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#e0e0e0\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Input -->\n        <rect x=\"50\" y=\"400\" width=\"140\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"120\" y=\"425\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Noisy Latent z_t</text>\n        <text x=\"120\" y=\"440\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">(4 \u00d7 64 \u00d7 64)</text>\n        <text x=\"120\" y=\"455\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d74\u00d764\u00d764</text>\n        \n        <!-- Encoder Down-blocks -->\n        <!-- Down-block 1 (64x64) -->\n        <rect x=\"250\" y=\"350\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#ffeaa7\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Down-block 1</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"390\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">64\u00d764, 320ch</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"405\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">ResBlock</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"420\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d7320\u00d764\u00d764</text>\n        \n        <!-- Down-block 2 (32x32) -->\n        <rect x=\"250\" y=\"500\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#ffeaa7\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"525\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Down-block 2</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"540\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">32\u00d732, 640ch</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"555\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">ResBlock + Cross-Attn</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"570\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d7640\u00d732\u00d732</text>\n        \n        <!-- Down-block 3 (16x16) -->\n        <rect x=\"250\" y=\"650\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#ffeaa7\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"675\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Down-block 3</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"690\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">16\u00d716, 1280ch</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"705\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">ResBlock + Cross-Attn</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"720\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d71280\u00d716\u00d716</text>\n        \n        <!-- Down-block 4 (8x8) -->\n        <rect x=\"250\" y=\"800\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#ffeaa7\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"825\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Down-block 4</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"840\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">8\u00d78, 1280ch</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"855\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">ResBlock</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"870\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d71280\u00d78\u00d78</text>\n        \n        <!-- Mid-block (bottleneck) -->\n        <rect x=\"450\" y=\"800\" width=\"140\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#fd79a8\" stroke=\"#e84393\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"520\" y=\"825\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Mid-block</text>\n        <text x=\"520\" y=\"840\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">8\u00d78, 1280ch</text>\n        <text x=\"520\" y=\"855\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">ResBlock + Cross-Attn</text>\n        <text x=\"520\" y=\"870\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d71280\u00d78\u00d78</text>\n        \n        <!-- Decoder Up-blocks -->\n        <!-- Up-block 1 (8x8) -->\n        <rect x=\"650\" y=\"800\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#a29bfe\" stroke=\"#6c5ce7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"825\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Up-block 1</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"840\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">8\u00d78, 1280ch</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"855\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">ResBlock</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"870\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d71280\u00d78\u00d78</text>\n        \n        <!-- Up-block 2 (16x16) -->\n        <rect x=\"650\" y=\"650\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#a29bfe\" stroke=\"#6c5ce7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"675\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Up-block 2</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"690\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">16\u00d716, 1280ch</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"705\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">ResBlock + Cross-Attn</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"720\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d71280\u00d716\u00d716</text>\n        \n        <!-- Up-block 3 (32x32) -->\n        <rect x=\"650\" y=\"500\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#a29bfe\" stroke=\"#6c5ce7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"525\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Up-block 3</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"540\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">32\u00d732, 640ch</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"555\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">ResBlock + Cross-Attn</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"570\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d7640\u00d732\u00d732</text>\n        \n        <!-- Up-block 4 (64x64) -->\n        <rect x=\"650\" y=\"350\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#a29bfe\" stroke=\"#6c5ce7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Up-block 4</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"390\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">64\u00d764, 320ch</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"405\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">ResBlock</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"420\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d7320\u00d764\u00d764</text>\n        \n        <!-- Output -->\n        <rect x=\"850\" y=\"400\" width=\"140\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"920\" y=\"425\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Predicted Noise</text>\n        <text x=\"920\" y=\"440\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">\u03b5_\u03b8</text>\n        <text x=\"920\" y=\"455\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d74\u00d764\u00d764</text>\n        \n        <!-- Timestep Conditioning -->\n        <rect x=\"1050\" y=\"100\" width=\"180\" height=\"120\" fill=\"#dda0dd\" stroke=\"#9932cc\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"1140\" y=\"125\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Timestep t</text>\n        <text x=\"1140\" y=\"145\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">\u2193</text>\n        <text x=\"1140\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">Sinusoidal Embedding</text>\n        <text x=\"1140\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">\u2193</text>\n        <text x=\"1140\" y=\"195\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">MLP</text>\n        <text x=\"1140\" y=\"210\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d71280</text>\n        \n        <!-- Text Conditioning -->\n        <rect x=\"1300\" y=\"100\" width=\"180\" height=\"120\" fill=\"#98fb98\" stroke=\"#32cd32\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"1390\" y=\"125\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Text Prompt</text>\n        <text x=\"1390\" y=\"145\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">\u2193</text>\n        <text x=\"1390\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">CLIP Text Encoder</text>\n        <text x=\"1390\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">\u2193</text>\n        <text x=\"1390\" y=\"195\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">Text Embeddings</text>\n        <text x=\"1390\" y=\"210\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d777\u00d7768</text>\n        \n        <!-- Main flow arrows -->\n        <path d=\"M 190 440 L 240 440\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 370 400 L 370 490\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 370 600 L 370 640\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 370 750 L 370 790\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 370 850 L 440 850\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 590 850 L 640 850\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 710 790 L 710 760\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 710 640 L 710 610\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 710 490 L 710 460\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 770 440 L 840 440\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Skip connections -->\n        <path d=\"M 370 400 Q 500 300 640 400\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 370 550 Q 500 450 640 550\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 370 700 Q 500 600 640 700\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 370 850 Q 500 750 640 850\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Timestep injection arrows -->\n        <path d=\"M 1050 160 L 320 380\" stroke=\"#9932cc\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-purple)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 1050 180 L 320 530\" stroke=\"#9932cc\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-purple)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 1050 200 L 320 680\" stroke=\"#9932cc\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-purple)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 1050 220 L 320 830\" stroke=\"#9932cc\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-purple)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 1050 240 L 520 830\" stroke=\"#9932cc\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-purple)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 1050 260 L 720 830\" stroke=\"#9932cc\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-purple)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 1050 280 L 720 680\" stroke=\"#9932cc\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-purple)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 1050 300 L 720 530\" stroke=\"#9932cc\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-purple)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 1050 320 L 720 380\" stroke=\"#9932cc\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-purple)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Cross-attention arrows -->\n        <path d=\"M 1300 180 L 320 530\" stroke=\"#32cd32\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 1300 200 L 320 680\" stroke=\"#32cd32\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 1300 220 L 520 830\" stroke=\"#32cd32\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 1300 240 L 720 830\" stroke=\"#32cd32\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 1300 260 L 720 680\" stroke=\"#32cd32\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 1300 280 L 720 530\" stroke=\"#32cd32\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Legend -->\n        <rect x=\"1550\" y=\"300\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" fill=\"#f8f9fa\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"1700\" y=\"325\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">LEGEND</text>\n        \n        <!-- Legend items -->\n        <rect x=\"1570\" y=\"340\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#ffeaa7\" stroke=\"#f39c12\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"355\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Encoder Down-blocks</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1570\" y=\"370\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#a29bfe\" stroke=\"#6c5ce7\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"385\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Decoder Up-blocks</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1570\" y=\"400\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#fd79a8\" stroke=\"#e84393\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"415\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Mid-block (bottleneck)</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1570\" y=\"430\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"445\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Input/Output</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1570\" y=\"460\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#dda0dd\" stroke=\"#9932cc\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"475\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Timestep Conditioning</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1570\" y=\"490\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#98fb98\" stroke=\"#32cd32\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"505\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Text Conditioning</text>\n        \n        <line x1=\"1570\" y1=\"525\" x2=\"1600\" y2=\"525\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"530\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Main Flow</text>\n        \n        <line x1=\"1570\" y1=\"545\" x2=\"1600\" y2=\"545\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"550\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Skip Connections</text>\n        \n        <line x1=\"1570\" y1=\"565\" x2=\"1600\" y2=\"565\" stroke=\"#9932cc\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"570\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Timestep Injection</text>\n        \n        <line x1=\"1570\" y1=\"585\" x2=\"1600\" y2=\"585\" stroke=\"#32cd32\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,3\"/>\n        <text x=\"1610\" y=\"590\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Cross-Attention</text>\n        \n        <text x=\"1570\" y=\"620\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Block Types:</text>\n        <text x=\"1570\" y=\"635\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#34495e\">\u2022 ResBlock: Basic residual block</text>\n        <text x=\"1570\" y=\"650\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#34495e\">\u2022 ResBlock + Cross-Attn:</text>\n        <text x=\"1580\" y=\"665\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#34495e\">  Residual + text attention</text>\n        \n        <!-- Arrow markers -->\n        <defs>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n            </marker>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead-red\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#e74c3c\"/>\n            </marker>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead-purple\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#9932cc\"/>\n            </marker>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead-green\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#32cd32\"/>\n            </marker>\n        </defs>\n    </svg>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Latent Diffusion U-Net</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"title\">Latent Diffusion U-Net (with conditioning)</div>\n    \n    <svg width=\"1880\" height=\"1000\" viewBox=\"0 0 1880 1000\">\n        <!-- Background -->\n        <rect width=\"1880\" height=\"1000\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#e0e0e0\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Input -->\n        <rect x=\"50\" y=\"400\" width=\"140\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"120\" y=\"425\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Noisy Latent z_t</text>\n        <text x=\"120\" y=\"440\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">(4 \u00d7 64 \u00d7 64)</text>\n        <text x=\"120\" y=\"455\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d74\u00d764\u00d764</text>\n        \n        <!-- Encoder Down-blocks -->\n        <!-- Down-block 1 (64x64) -->\n        <rect x=\"250\" y=\"350\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#ffeaa7\" stroke=\"#fdcb6e\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Down-block 1</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"390\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">64\u00d764, 320ch</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"405\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">ResBlock</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"420\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d7320\u00d764\u00d764</text>\n        \n        <!-- Down-block 2 (32x32) -->\n        <rect x=\"250\" y=\"480\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#fab1a0\" stroke=\"#e17055\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"505\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Down-block 2</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"520\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">32\u00d732, 640ch</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"535\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">ResBlock + Cross-Attn</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"550\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d7640\u00d732\u00d732</text>\n        \n        <!-- Down-block 3 (16x16) -->\n        <rect x=\"250\" y=\"610\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#fd79a8\" stroke=\"#e84393\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"635\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Down-block 3</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"650\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">16\u00d716, 1280ch</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"665\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">ResBlock + Cross-Attn</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"680\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d71280\u00d716\u00d716</text>\n        \n        <!-- Down-block 4 (8x8) -->\n        <rect x=\"250\" y=\"740\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#a29bfe\" stroke=\"#6c5ce7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"765\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Down-block 4</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"780\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">8\u00d78, 1280ch</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"795\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">ResBlock</text>\n        <text x=\"310\" y=\"810\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d71280\u00d78\u00d78</text>\n        \n        <!-- Mid-block (bottleneck) -->\n        <rect x=\"450\" y=\"740\" width=\"140\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#ff7675\" stroke=\"#d63031\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"520\" y=\"765\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Mid-block</text>\n        <text x=\"520\" y=\"780\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">8\u00d78, 1280ch</text>\n        <text x=\"520\" y=\"795\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">ResBlock + Cross-Attn</text>\n        <text x=\"520\" y=\"810\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d71280\u00d78\u00d78</text>\n        \n        <!-- Decoder Up-blocks -->\n        <!-- Up-block 1 (8x8) -->\n        <rect x=\"650\" y=\"740\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#a29bfe\" stroke=\"#6c5ce7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"765\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Up-block 1</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"780\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">8\u00d78, 1280ch</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"795\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">ResBlock</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"810\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d71280\u00d78\u00d78</text>\n        \n        <!-- Up-block 2 (16x16) -->\n        <rect x=\"650\" y=\"610\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#fd79a8\" stroke=\"#e84393\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"635\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Up-block 2</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"650\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">16\u00d716, 1280ch</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"665\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">ResBlock + Cross-Attn</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"680\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d71280\u00d716\u00d716</text>\n        \n        <!-- Up-block 3 (32x32) -->\n        <rect x=\"650\" y=\"480\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#fab1a0\" stroke=\"#e17055\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"505\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Up-block 3</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"520\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">32\u00d732, 640ch</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"535\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">ResBlock + Cross-Attn</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"550\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d7640\u00d732\u00d732</text>\n        \n        <!-- Up-block 4 (64x64) -->\n        <rect x=\"650\" y=\"350\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#ffeaa7\" stroke=\"#fdcb6e\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Up-block 4</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"390\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">64\u00d764, 320ch</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"405\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">ResBlock</text>\n        <text x=\"710\" y=\"420\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d7320\u00d764\u00d764</text>\n        \n        <!-- Output -->\n        <rect x=\"830\" y=\"400\" width=\"140\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"900\" y=\"425\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Predicted Noise</text>\n        <text x=\"900\" y=\"440\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">\u03b5_\u03b8 (4 \u00d7 64 \u00d7 64)</text>\n        <text x=\"900\" y=\"455\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d74\u00d764\u00d764</text>\n        \n        <!-- Timestep conditioning -->\n        <rect x=\"50\" y=\"150\" width=\"200\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#dcedc1\" stroke=\"#6ab04c\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"150\" y=\"175\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Timestep t</text>\n        <text x=\"150\" y=\"190\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">\u2192 sinusoidal embedding</text>\n        <text x=\"150\" y=\"205\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">\u2192 MLP</text>\n        <text x=\"150\" y=\"220\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d7320</text>\n        \n        <!-- Text conditioning -->\n        <rect x=\"300\" y=\"150\" width=\"200\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#fad5d5\" stroke=\"#eb4d4b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"400\" y=\"175\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Text Prompt</text>\n        <text x=\"400\" y=\"190\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">\u2192 CLIP Text Encoder</text>\n        <text x=\"400\" y=\"205\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#34495e\">\u2192 Context Embeddings</text>\n        <text x=\"400\" y=\"220\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\">B\u00d777\u00d7768</text>\n        \n        <!-- Main flow arrows -->\n        <!-- Input to Down-block 1 -->\n        <path d=\"M 190 440 L 240 400\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Down-blocks connections -->\n        <path d=\"M 310 450 L 310 470\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 310 580 L 310 600\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 310 710 L 310 730\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Down-block 4 to Mid-block -->\n        <path d=\"M 370 790 L 440 790\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Mid-block to Up-block 1 -->\n        <path d=\"M 590 790 L 640 790\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Up-blocks connections -->\n        <path d=\"M 710 730 L 710 710\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 710 600 L 710 580\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 710 470 L 710 450\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Up-block 4 to Output -->\n        <path d=\"M 770 400 L 820 440\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Skip connections -->\n        <path d=\"M 370 400 Q 500 300 640 400\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-purple)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 370 530 Q 500 430 640 530\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-purple)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 370 660 Q 500 560 640 660\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-purple)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 370 790 Q 500 690 640 790\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-purple)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Timestep injection arrows -->\n        <path d=\"M 150 230 L 280 340\" stroke=\"#6ab04c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 150 230 L 280 470\" stroke=\"#6ab04c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 150 230 L 280 600\" stroke=\"#6ab04c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 150 230 L 280 730\" stroke=\"#6ab04c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 150 230 L 480 730\" stroke=\"#6ab04c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 150 230 L 680 730\" stroke=\"#6ab04c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 150 230 L 680 600\" stroke=\"#6ab04c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 150 230 L 680 470\" stroke=\"#6ab04c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 150 230 L 680 340\" stroke=\"#6ab04c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Cross-attention arrows -->\n        <path d=\"M 400 230 L 280 470\" stroke=\"#eb4d4b\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 400 230 L 280 600\" stroke=\"#eb4d4b\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 400 230 L 480 730\" stroke=\"#eb4d4b\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 400 230 L 680 600\" stroke=\"#eb4d4b\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 400 230 L 680 470\" stroke=\"#eb4d4b\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Legend -->\n        <rect x=\"1100\" y=\"150\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" fill=\"#f8f9fa\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n        <text x=\"1250\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">LEGEND</text>\n        \n        <!-- Legend items -->\n        <rect x=\"1120\" y=\"200\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#ffeaa7\" stroke=\"#fdcb6e\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1160\" y=\"215\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">ResBlock only (64\u00d764, 8\u00d78)</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1120\" y=\"230\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#fab1a0\" stroke=\"#e17055\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1160\" y=\"245\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">ResBlock + Cross-Attn (32\u00d732)</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1120\" y=\"260\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#fd79a8\" stroke=\"#e84393\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1160\" y=\"275\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">ResBlock + Cross-Attn (16\u00d716)</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1120\" y=\"290\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#a29bfe\" stroke=\"#6c5ce7\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1160\" y=\"305\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Up/Down blocks (8\u00d78)</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1120\" y=\"320\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#ff7675\" stroke=\"#d63031\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1160\" y=\"335\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Mid-block (bottleneck)</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1120\" y=\"350\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#e8f4fd\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1160\" y=\"365\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Input/Output tensors</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1120\" y=\"380\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#dcedc1\" stroke=\"#6ab04c\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1160\" y=\"395\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Timestep conditioning</text>\n        \n        <rect x=\"1120\" y=\"410\" width=\"30\" height=\"20\" fill=\"#fad5d5\" stroke=\"#eb4d4b\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"1160\" y=\"425\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Text conditioning</text>\n        \n        <!-- Arrow legend -->\n        <line x1=\"1120\" y1=\"450\" x2=\"1150\" y2=\"450\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <text x=\"1160\" y=\"455\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Main data flow</text>\n        \n        <line x1=\"1120\" y1=\"470\" x2=\"1150\" y2=\"470\" stroke=\"#9b59b6\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-purple)\"/>\n        <text x=\"1160\" y=\"475\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Skip connections</text>\n        \n        <line x1=\"1120\" y1=\"490\" x2=\"1150\" y2=\"490\" stroke=\"#6ab04c\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n        <text x=\"1160\" y=\"495\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Timestep injection</text>\n        \n        <line x1=\"1120\" y1=\"510\" x2=\"1150\" y2=\"510\" stroke=\"#eb4d4b\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-red)\"/>\n        <text x=\"1160\" y=\"515\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#2c3e50\">Cross-attention</text>\n        \n        <!-- Arrow markers -->\n        <defs>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n            </marker>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead-purple\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#9b59b6\"/>\n            </marker>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead-green\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#6ab04c\"/>\n            </marker>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead-red\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#eb4d4b\"/>\n            </marker>\n        </defs>\n        \n        <!-- Labels for skip connections -->\n        <text x=\"500\" y=\"290\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" font-weight=\"bold\">Skip</text>\n        <text x=\"500\" y=\"420\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" font-weight=\"bold\">Skip</text>\n        <text x=\"500\" y=\"550\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" font-weight=\"bold\">Skip</text>\n        <text x=\"500\" y=\"680\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" font-weight=\"bold\">Skip</text>\n        \n    </svg>\n</body>\n</html>"}